;Additional musicians
*Meia Noite – percussion
*Ljubomir Dimitrijević – kaval, gemshorn, zurla, gajde, dvojnice, bagpipes, flutes on &quot;Execution Style&quot;, &quot;Born Again Anarchist&quot;, &quot;Soulfly IV&quot;
