<doc id="603611" wikidata="Q7967490" url="?curid=603611" title="Wang Jinping (sprinter)">
<text>Wang Jinping (, born 7 March 1987, in Heilongjiang) is a female Chinese athletics sprinter, who represented her country at the 4 × 400 m relay event at the 2008 Summer Olympics.

